# Content Studio Frontend Module

This module contains the first frontend authoring foundation for Content Studio.

It includes:
- backend-aligned contract types
- a typed API client boundary
- document list and create UI
- a simple draft editor shell with block save and publish actions

It intentionally does not include drag-and-drop, slash commands, collaborative editing, media uploads, assessment behavior, or cross-stack E2E coverage.
